{"id":198,"ayahs":[{"number":69,"arabic":"كَٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبْلِكُمْ كَانُوٓا۟ أَشَدَّ مِنكُمْ قُوَّةًۭ وَأَكْثَرَ أَمْوَٰلًۭا وَأَوْلَٰدًۭا فَٱسْتَمْتَعُوا۟ بِخَلَٰقِهِمْ فَٱسْتَمْتَعْتُم بِخَلَٰقِكُمْ كَمَا ٱسْتَمْتَعَ ٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبْلِكُم بِخَلَٰقِهِمْ وَخُضْتُمْ كَٱلَّذِى خَاضُوٓا۟ ۚ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ حَبِطَتْ أَعْمَٰلُهُمْ فِى ٱلدُّنْيَا وَٱلْءَاخِرَةِ ۖ وَأُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلْخَٰسِرُونَ","translation":"[Say unto them: \"You are] like those [hypocrites] who lived before your time. Greater than you were they in power, and richer in wealth and in children; and they enjoyed their share [of happiness]. And you have been enjoying your share -just as those who preceded you enjoyed their share; and you have been indulging in scurrilous talk -just as they indulged in it. It is they whose works have come to nought in this world and in the life to come - and it is they, they who are the cost!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1304.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":59127,"position":1,"arabic":"كَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) মতো যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59128,"position":2,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59129,"position":3,"arabic":"قَبْلِكُمْ","translation":"পূর্ব তোমাদের(ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59130,"position":4,"arabic":"كَانُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59131,"position":5,"arabic":"أَشَدَّ","translation":"প্রবলতর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59132,"position":6,"arabic":"مِنكُمْ","translation":"চেয়ে তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59133,"position":7,"arabic":"قُوَّةًۭ","translation":"শক্তিতে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59134,"position":8,"arabic":"وَأَكْثَرَ","translation":"ও অধিক","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59135,"position":9,"arabic":"أَمْوَٰلًۭا","translation":"ধনসম্পদে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59136,"position":10,"arabic":"وَأَوْلَـٰدًۭا","translation":"ও সন্তান-সন্তুতিতে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59137,"position":11,"arabic":"فَٱسْتَمْتَعُوا۟","translation":"অতঃপর তারা ভোগ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59138,"position":12,"arabic":"بِخَلَـٰقِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59139,"position":13,"arabic":"فَٱسْتَمْتَعْتُم","translation":"এখন তোমরা ভোগ করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59140,"position":14,"arabic":"بِخَلَـٰقِكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59141,"position":15,"arabic":"كَمَا","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59142,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱسْتَمْتَعَ","translation":"ভোগ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59143,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59144,"position":18,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59145,"position":19,"arabic":"قَبْلِكُم","translation":"পূর্ব তোমাদের (ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59146,"position":20,"arabic":"بِخَلَـٰقِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59147,"position":21,"arabic":"وَخُضْتُمْ","translation":"ও তোমরা আলাপ-আলোচনা করেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59148,"position":22,"arabic":"كَٱلَّذِى","translation":"মতো তাদের যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59149,"position":23,"arabic":"خَاضُوٓا۟ ۚ","translation":"তারা আলাপ-আলোচনা করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59151,"position":24,"arabic":"أُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"ঐসব লোকের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59152,"position":25,"arabic":"حَبِطَتْ","translation":"নষ্ট হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59153,"position":26,"arabic":"أَعْمَـٰلُهُمْ","translation":"কাজকর্ম তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59154,"position":27,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59155,"position":28,"arabic":"ٱلدُّنْيَا","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59156,"position":29,"arabic":"وَٱلْـَٔاخِرَةِ ۖ","translation":"এবং আখেরাতেও","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59158,"position":30,"arabic":"وَأُو۟لَـٰٓئِكَ","translation":"এবং ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59159,"position":31,"arabic":"هُمُ","translation":"তারাই","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59160,"position":32,"arabic":"ٱلْخَـٰسِرُونَ","translation":"ক্ষতিগ্রস্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/009_069_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59161,"position":33,"arabic":"٦٩","translation":"(৬৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":70,"arabic":"أَلَمْ يَأْتِهِمْ نَبَأُ ٱلَّذِينَ مِن قَبْلِهِمْ قَوْمِ نُوحٍۢ وَعَادٍۢ وَثَمُودَ وَقَوْمِ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَأَصْحَٰبِ مَدْيَنَ وَٱلْمُؤْتَفِكَٰتِ ۚ أَتَتْهُمْ رُسُلُهُم بِٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ ۖ فَمَا كَانَ ٱللَّهُ لِيَظْلِمَهُمْ وَلَٰكِن كَانُوٓا۟ أَنفُسَهُمْ يَظْلِمُونَ","translation":"Have, then, the stories of those who preceded them never come within the ken of these [hypocrites and deniers of the truth]?-[the stories] of Noah's people, and of [the tribes of] `Ad and Thamud, and of Abraham's people, and of the folk of Madyan, and of the cities that were overthrown? To [all of] them their apostles had come with all evidence of the truth. [but they rejected them:] and so it was not God who wronged them [by His punishment], but it was they who wronged themselves.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1305.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":59396,"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","translation":"কি নি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59397,"position":2,"arabic":"يَأْتِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের কাছে আসে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59398,"position":3,"arabic":"نَبَأُ","translation":"সংবাদ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59399,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"(তাদের) যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59400,"position":5,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59401,"position":6,"arabic":"قَبْلِهِمْ","translation":"পূর্ব তাদের(ছিলো)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59402,"position":7,"arabic":"قَوْمِ","translation":"(যেমন) জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59403,"position":8,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","translation":"নূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59404,"position":9,"arabic":"وَعَادٍۢ","translation":"ও আদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59405,"position":10,"arabic":"وَثَمُودَ","translation":"ও সামুদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59406,"position":11,"arabic":"وَقَوْمِ","translation":"ও জাতি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59407,"position":12,"arabic":"إِبْرَٰهِيمَ","translation":"ইবরাহীমের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59408,"position":13,"arabic":"وَأَصْحَـٰبِ","translation":"ও অধিবাসী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59409,"position":14,"arabic":"مَدْيَنَ","translation":"মাদইয়ানের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59410,"position":15,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْتَفِكَـٰتِ ۚ","translation":"ও বিধ্বস্ত নগরের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59412,"position":16,"arabic":"أَتَتْهُمْ","translation":"তাদের কাছে এসেছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59413,"position":17,"arabic":"رُسُلُهُم","translation":"রাসূলরা তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59414,"position":18,"arabic":"بِٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ ۖ","translation":"নিয়ে সুস্পষ্ট নিদর্শন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59416,"position":19,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"অতঃপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59417,"position":20,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"নন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59418,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ (এমন যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59419,"position":22,"arabic":"لِيَظْلِمَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের উপর অবিচার করবেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59420,"position":23,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِن","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59421,"position":24,"arabic":"كَانُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা ছিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59422,"position":25,"arabic":"أَنفُسَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের নিজেদের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59423,"position":26,"arabic":"يَظْلِمُونَ","translation":"অবিচার করতো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_070_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59424,"position":27,"arabic":"٧٠","translation":"(৭০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":71,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ وَٱلْمُؤْمِنَٰتُ بَعْضُهُمْ أَوْلِيَآءُ بَعْضٍۢ ۚ يَأْمُرُونَ بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ وَيَنْهَوْنَ عَنِ ٱلْمُنكَرِ وَيُقِيمُونَ ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ وَيُؤْتُونَ ٱلزَّكَوٰةَ وَيُطِيعُونَ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥٓ ۚ أُو۟لَٰٓئِكَ سَيَرْحَمُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ ۗ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ عَزِيزٌ حَكِيمٌۭ","translation":"AND [as for] the believers, both men and women they are close unto one another: they [all] enjoin the doing of what is right and forbid the doing of what is wrong, and are constant in prayer, and render the purifying dues, and pay heed unto God and His Apostle. It is they upon whom God will bestow His grace: verily, God is almighty, wise!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1306.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":60063,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"এবং মু'মিন পুরুষ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60064,"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُؤْمِنَـٰتُ","translation":"মু'মিন নারী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60065,"position":3,"arabic":"بَعْضُهُمْ","translation":"একে তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60066,"position":4,"arabic":"أَوْلِيَآءُ","translation":"বন্ধু","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60067,"position":5,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ ۚ","translation":"অপরের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60069,"position":6,"arabic":"يَأْمُرُونَ","translation":"তারা নির্দেশ দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60070,"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱلْمَعْرُوفِ","translation":"ব্যাপারে সৎকাজের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60071,"position":8,"arabic":"وَيَنْهَوْنَ","translation":"ও তারা নিষেধ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60072,"position":9,"arabic":"عَنِ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60073,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱلْمُنكَرِ","translation":"অন্যায় কাজ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60074,"position":11,"arabic":"وَيُقِيمُونَ","translation":"ও প্রতিষ্ঠা করে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_071_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60075,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱلصَّلَوٰةَ","translation":"সালাত","audioUrl":